{"tid":1760504,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[月經文] 二手 mon 邊度買好?","createTime":"2019-11-28T09:06:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T14:01:51.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aedb74129ff9bdf2894d0441903205a75c694f76","tid":1760504,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:06:27.000Z","msg":"原先用緊12吋闊 嘅方形mon (6:4?)，橫向超過12吋的要把嗽叭橫放mon 頂。<br />\n<br />\n上年打算整得就整原則，原有mon 整過一次，但都係收皮，所以決定唔再整，直接攞去回收。<br />\n<del><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">(呻下: 要自己扲去回收商都坐幾遠下車，唔係環保心理過意質素無要求。 </span></span></strong></del><br />\n<br />\n有打機有睇片，但對質素無要求。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"><del>6:4都頂到嘅人，點會特登要求2k/4k</del></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">除咗死點外，買2手mon 有咩要注意?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實買得2手mon,有幾點死點唔太誇張都預咗。(無就緊係正啦)<br />\n<br />\n2手JJ覺得對畫質無要求嘅話，2手嘢真係平靚正又環保。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a978986580dd9739289a5a94991120a986c08a3c","tid":1760504,"uid":28668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:10:51.000Z","msg":"一係dcfever 唔啱就轉身走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n網上都search到有啲會有賣 有鋪面係深水埗"},{"pid":"6678bb1b85f943e51fe59e9c9039e519d484c5f0","tid":1760504,"uid":138809,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"方形mon in 2019 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal